Client Access | BNY Mellon

















































 






















Client Access            
BNY Mellon provides you with the tools you need to monitor and manage your assets. Through our innovative and intuitive technology, including investment portals, mobile trading platforms, transactional apps and more, you can access assets right at your fingertips.








Alternative Investments





Hedge Fund Clients
Manage and access portfolio and investor level data through reports and downloadable extracts.
Access Hedge Fund




Fund of Hedge Fund Clients
Manage and access portfolio and investor level data through reports and downloadable extracts.
Access Fund of Hedge Fund




Investors
Easy access to your account information including statements, confirms, NAVs & returns, management letters and company profiles.
Access Investor







Asset Servicing 





Client Learning Management System (CLMS)
Our user friendly platform provides you with on-line, real-time access to educational opportunities ranging from webinars to on-demand sessions. 
Access CLMS 




Workbench
Workbench facilitates the investment life cycle from decision-making to execution, settlement and reporting.
Access Workbench




INFORM
INFORM provides information on custody, accounting, settlement and related activity.
Access INFORM




Benefit Disbursements
BNY Mellon’s Benefit Disbursements site is designed for individuals who are currently receiving pension payments issued by BNY Mellon.
Access Benefit Disbursements Information







Capital Markets U.S.





BNY Mellon Capital Markets, LLC
Through BNY Mellon Capital Markets, LLC, we also offer trading in fixed income securities and equities.
Access Capital Markets




BNY Mellon Structured Solutions
BNY Mellon Structured Solutions provides real-time access to educational training modules, our product suite, regulatory updates, user friendly search tools and marketing materials.
Access Structured Solutions







Corporate Trust





Investor Reporting
You can access detailed payment and collateral reporting data on our Investor Reporting site.
Access Investor Reporting




INFORM
Accounting, cash management, online corporate actions: With INFORM, BNY Mellon's proprietary information delivery and transaction management system.
ACCESS INFORM




Money Market Manager
Originate commercial paper issuance and medium-term note transactions, and generate the reports you need to manage these debt instruments on our Money Market Manager system.
Access MMI System







Depositary Receipts





ADR INFORM
As the world's leading depositary bank, BNY Mellon has long recognized the importance of developing and integrating innovative technology with the evolving Depositary Receipt business. 
Access ADR INFORM







Foreign Exchange





iFX Manager
iFX Manager, BNY Mellon's proprietary electronic trading system, supports pre-trade order management, price discovery and execution services.
Access iFX Manager




iConfirm
iConfirm offers post-trade confirmation, standing settlement instruction maintenance and mark-to-market reporting.
Access iConfirm




iHedge
iHedge is designed to help clients administer portfolio or shareclass hedging programs.
Access iHedge




iDeal Forex
iDeal Forex is a platform for multicurrency payment initiation, FX trade execution and related reporting.
Access iDeal Forex




iFlow
iFlow measures cross-border portfolio flow and provides tools to measure capital flows against most major equity and fixed income indices.
Access iFlow







Liquidity Services





Liquidity DIRECTSM
Access a multi-currency cash management portal that provides a wide range of money market funds, individual money market securities and the capabilities to manage margin balances.
Access Liquidity Services







Treasury Services





TreasuryEdge
Initiate a full range of transactions to manage available cash balances using our simple but powerful electronic banking solution.
Access TreasuryEdge







Wealth Management





Private Workbench
Instant access to your BNY Mellon Wealth Management relationship and financial reporting.
Access Private Workbench




Business Banking
Access your business account information.
Business Online Banking




Mortgage
View your mortgage information and payment activity, make one-time payments, download statements, and more.
Mortgage Online Portal













 















